  "intent_precise": "Illumina DNA Prep Part 4, Clean Up Libraries First Half: Using thermo_tubes (labware, slot 3), sample_plate (plate, slot 2), midi_plate_2 (deep_well_plate, slot 3), midi_plate_1 (deep_well_plate, slot 6). With temperature module, magnetic module. (1) Transfer from source (multiple wells) to destination (multiple wells). (2) Transfer 70\u00b5L from source to destination. (3) Engage magnets for bead separation. (4) Incubate for 5 minutes. (5) Transfer from source to destination. (6) Disengage magnets to release beads. (7) Transfer from source to destination. (8) Transfer 45\u00b5L from source to destination. (9) Mix 10 times at 100\u00b5L. (10) Incubate for 5 minutes.",
